I"ª<p>Our group focuses on machine learning and computer vision research. Research topics currently studied in our group are:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Deep generative modelling</li>
  <li>Compact and power-efficient deep neural networks for edge intelligence</li>
  <li>CNN-generated image detection</li>
  <li>Few shot learning</li>
</ul>

